   LA-SCHOOL-CHEATS _ (Los Angeles) Glendale residents Danny
Khatchaturian and Dikran Ishendorian once wanted to become
top-flight lawyers. Now they need one. Prosecutors in Los Angeles
are accusing the pair of devising a complicated scheme to ace a law
school entrance exam _ using forged student identification, a
stolen test booklet and pager transmissions across the Pacific
Ocean. By Peter Hartlaub. (Will move in the ``n'' California and
