<HEADLINE>
PILOTS UNION IN CONTEMPT, FINED $10 MILLION
</HEADLINE>
  
 (ATTN: Texas, Ill., Minn., Fla., N.Y., Colo.)   (Eds: Also moving in `a' category.) 
(jw) 
