   GINGRICH-LEGACY _ Although Newt Gingrich tried to distance
himself from it at the end, the failed impeachment effort is the
last legacy of his tenure as speaker. But the ex-speaker is already
making good progress in leaving the whole mess behind. (Sherman,
Atlanta Journal-Constitution).
