MEXICO-DRUGS a reefer; all stories have moved, except
IMPEACH-TRIAL, which is expected to move by 3:15 p.m..) 
<TEXT>
<P>
   Here are the stories that New York Times editors are planning
for the Page 1 of Sunday, Feb. 14. The N.Y. Times News Service
supervisor is Ned Kilkelly.
</P>
<P>
   For copy info: (212) 556-1927.
</P>
<P>
   For graphics, map, photo info: (212) 556-4204.
</P>
