   IMPEACHMENT FOLLOWUPS
</P>
<P>
   CLINTON-NEXT _ WASHINGTON _ Now that the impeachment cloud has
been lifted, how effectively can President Clinton govern? He'll be
a lame-duck president facing an opposition-led Congress, and his
poll numbers may drop without anti-impeachment sentiment to prop
them up. Still, Clinton may find politically bruised Republicans
willing to meet him more than halfway on policy. (Deans, Cox News
Service). MOVED
</P>
