no longer a prisoner of war, but for the next two years he'll play
one on TV. And in the newpapers. And on radio. And billboards. And
bumper stickers. And campaign buttons. And so on. The one thing
McCain desparately wants to become _ president _ is completely
dependant on the one thing McCain desparately wanted to avoid
becoming _ a POW. By E.J. MONTINI Story will move in the ``A'' and
``K'' categories. &QL; 
